**Gap 2 — Dual generator signature conflict:**
```python
# V3 signature
MashetGenerator.generate(substrates: Set[str], concept: str) -> MashetWord

# Feedback Loops expects
generator.generate(concept: str) -> MashetWord

# Resolution — unified optional-substrate signature
class UnifiedMashetGenerator:
    def generate(self, 
                 concept: str,
                 substrates: Optional[Set[str]] = None) -> MashetWord:
        if substrates is None:
            analysis = self.analyzer.analyze_deep(concept)
            substrates = set(analysis['substrates'].keys())
        return self._generate_from_substrates(substrates, concept)
```

